Title: Flume feat. Toro y Moi - The Difference (“Hi This is Paint” Visualizer by Spinning Rock)
Description:
"Hi This Is Paint” was a real-time collaborative painting by Spinning Rock. It was inspired by The Difference by Flume feat. Toro y Moi, existing creative developed by Jonathan Zawada, and Reddit’s r/place, and r/flume. The experience was live for 72 hours with participation from 6,140 people across 46 countries, raising money for the Equal Justice Initiative.

You can read more about the experiment here: https://spinningrock.com/htip/

You can try it out here: http://flume.spinningrock.com.s3-website.us-east-2.amazonaws.com
